divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing in my back yard with the dog staring at the night sky when an apparent triangular ship headed South West across viewable sky at high speed with no sound aproximately 40 degrees from horizon.Impossible to be a Jet or Airplane do to the speed of passing with lack of sound though area is between several airports.Object transversed the viewable sky in less the 10 seconds.Object obscurred stars as it passed between them and I
Summary: Either 3 objects in a triangular formation or triangular ship headed South West across viewable sky at high speed with no sound
